reviewText: This is four movies on one disk. The quality is quite poor. One of the movies won't work at all. The others have extremely low sound quality.
I bought this solely for look who's talking now because that movie by itself is actually a little more than this 4 pack. The others were just a bonus :)
Four movies - good quality. Benji and Karate Dog were a bit dull and boring but Look Who's Talking Now was a hit with our whole family.
